                        &lt;p&gt;Hi Alin,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team decided to use same rules of Conway&#039;s Game of Life with 1 more rule coming from Pokemon game.  New added rule is, each time an Alive Cell dies, you get 1 candy, and once you have 100 candies, about 3 to 5 Alive Cells will pop-up randomly to invoke an &quot;Evolve&quot; just like in Pokemon game.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What do you think? :)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Regards.&lt;br/&gt;Mj&lt;/p&gt;                    </summary>

                                            <content type="html">
                            &lt;p&gt;Hi Alin,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team decided to use same rules of Conway&#039;s Game of Life with 1 more rule coming from Pokemon game.  New added rule is, each time an Alive Cell dies, you get 1 candy, and once you have 100 candies, about 3 to 5 Alive Cells will pop-up randomly to invoke an &quot;Evolve&quot; just like in Pokemon game.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What do you think? :)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Regards.&lt;br/&gt;Mj&lt;/p&gt;                        </content>
                    
