                    <title>Hello there,
If I understand…</title>
                    <link rel="alternate" href="http://coderetreat.org/xn/detail/6456126:Comment:55039"/>
                                        <id>tag:coderetreat.org,2016-09-20:6456126:Comment:55039</id>
